Description: Carleton East offers you the best of two worlds. There is the lush, green landscaped community with a suburban feel, yet it's located just minutes from downtown Washington D.C. Here you'll find garden style apartment homes with spacious layouts, modern kitchens and bathrooms, large light infusing windows and private balconies. Our beautiful community is also convenient to local business, NASA, the University of Maryland, Greenbelt National Park, 495/I-95, the Baltimore/Washington Parkway and the Metro. All-in-all, it's a wonderful place to come home to.

Description: The Gates of Cipriano Apartment Homes in Greenbelt, Maryland, has one, two and three-bedroom apartment homes, close to the Capitol Beltway, minutes from 295, I-95 and major expressways, the airport and Washington, DC, so commuting is easy. You can also leave your car at home and ride the Metro bus that stops in our community. Living in your spacious apartment home, you'll appreciate how easy it to go anywhere--work, sightseeing, shopping, dining or movies. On our grounds, you'll enjoy a state-of-the-art fitness center, resort-style swimming pool with sundeck, hot tub and grilling area. Our Internet Cafe and unique on-site daycare are very popular with residents. Come visit us today, and experience our luxurious retreat, surprisingly close to everything.
